overview: Tom is an architect, not totally satisfied with the fact he's becoming a father. He gets the assignment, with two fellow members, to collect the status of an abandoned old hospital, S:t Emilia's. Meanwhile, an arguing couple picks up a hitchhiker, and for unforeseen reasons , these six people gets stuck at the hospital. Strange things start to happen, and a diary is found. The little girl, Julia , can begin to tell her story.
title: De Utsatta
